https://01.org/linuxgraphics/forum/graphics-installer-discussions/why-cant-i-get-sound-through-hdmi-intel-nuc-ubuntu-16.04-nor  //---------*****************HDMI audio not working properly on APL NUC *********-------------------------------------------------
